1. Download VSCode (code.visualstudio.com)
-click on Download for Windows

2.Go to bootstrap and copy starter template
- go to (getbootstrap.com/docs/4.5/getting-started/introduction/)
-paste in your index.html file
-copy the JS script link (as well)
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ho+j7jyWK8fNQe+A12Hb8AhRq26LrZ/JpcUGGOn+Y7RsweNrtN/tE3MoK7ZeZDyx" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
-paste it before the body tag
-
3. Go to (google font family) fonts.google.com
-example (poppins and regular 400) and copy the embedded link and paste in your head tag of html
- copy the other info (CSS rules to specify families) example:font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;

4. In bootstrap we can pass (h1,h2,h3,h4,etc) as a a class to (p tag)

example <p> class="h1">Ghana is great</p>

5. Text muting - Ex: <p class="h1 text-muted"> This is the first time you are seeing this</p>

6.Display class : example (<p class="display-1"> My File</p>) we have (display- 1) to (display-4)

7. Align text - to center : <p class="text-center>This is my text</p>)

8. 7. Align text - to right : <p class="text-right>This is my text</p>)
9.  Align text - to left : <p class="text-left>This is my text</p>)
10. Unordered List tag
<ul>
   <li> One </li>
   <li> Two </li>
    <li> Three </li>
</ul>

11. Displaying unordered list in an inline
<ul class="list-inline">
   <li class="list-inline-item"> One </li>
   <li class="list-inline-item"> Two </li>
   <li class="list-inline-item"> Three </li>
</ul>

12. Grid system in Bootstrap

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
       <div class="col-md-4">
         <p>This is bootstrap</p>
       </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
                <p>This is bootstrap</p>
        </div>

         <div class="col-md-4">
                 <p>This is bootstrap</p>
           </div>
    </div>


     <div class="row">
           <div class="col-md-6">
             <p>This is bootstrap</p>
           </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                    <p>This is bootstrap</p>
            </div>

        </div>


</div>
OR

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
       <div class="col">
         <p>This is bootstrap</p>
       </div>
    </div>
</div>